# Overview

This tutorial describes how to use Prometheus Service to monitor applications and databases. For example, you can use Prometheus Service to monitor Java virtual machine \(JVM\) applications, Go applications, MySQL databases, and Redis databases. This tutorial also describes how to configure Grafana dashboards to display monitoring data.

